text: Okay, I have to ask, how come conservatives never took advantage of this hack to stop anything?

"You can stop the government in its tracks by just coughing gently."
"How come I never heard about that?"
"It wasn't needed before this year."
Everyone understands that the term 'woke right' is designed to return the GOP to the status of controlled opposition. Only question is whether you think that would be a good thing.
And the other half of this absurdly unbalanced kvetching comes from irate antisemites insisting MAGA is a Jewish conspiracy.
